---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CategoryGrid from '../components/CategoryGrid.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Russia Knowledge Base"
  description="An open-source, AI-friendly knowledge base about Russia: history, geography, culture, economy, society, and daily life."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Russia.md</p>
      <h1>Russia, in structured notes instead of stereotypes.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        This project builds a Russia-focused atlas:
        broad geography, layered history, regional culture, public institutions,
        technology, everyday life, and practical reference links for humans and LLM agents.
      </p>
      <p class="fork-note">
        This site is an explicit fork of <a href="https://github.com/frank890417/taiwan-md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">taiwan-md</a>,
        rebuilt around a Russia-specific corpus and deployed from
        <a href="https://github.com/denis-gordeev/russia-md" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> denis-gordeev/russia-md</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#categories" class="primary">Browse categories</a>
        <a href="/resources" class="secondary">Official resources</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div><strong>12</strong><span>categories</span></div>
        <div><strong>1</strong><span>starter essay each</span></div>
        <div><strong>1</strong><span>agent skills brief</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="intro-inner">
      <h2>What this fork is for</h2>
      <p>
        The goal is not to flatten Russia into a tourist brochure or a political slogan.
        It is to provide a reusable starting structure for a country knowledge base that
        can support reading, linking, search, and future agent workflows.
      </p>
      <p>
        The current version is intentionally narrow and clean: the upstream `taiwan-md` shell and category logic,
        a Russia-first content map, starter articles, and a separate <a href="https://github.com/denis-gordeev/russia-md/blob/main/SKILLS.md">`SKILLS.md`</a>
        brief for LLM-agent integrations such as Gosuslugi, VK, Yandex, DaData, and official data sources.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="categories" class="categories">
    <div class="section-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">Explore</p>
      <h2>Twelve ways into the country</h2>
    </div>
    <CategoryGrid />
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.7), transparent 35%),
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(252, 211, 77, 0.35), transparent 30%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #eef2ff 100%);
  }

  .hero-inner,
  .intro-inner,
  .section-head {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: #475569;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    max-width: 12ch;
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 720px;
    color: #334155;
  }

  .fork-note {
    max-width: 760px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #475569;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-actions a {
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .primary {
    background: #0f172a;
    color: white;
  }

  .secondary {
    background: white;
    color: #0f172a;
    border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-stats div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
  }

  .hero-stats strong {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .hero-stats span {
    color: #475569;
  }

  .intro,
  .categories {
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem 3rem;
  }

  .intro p {
    max-width: 760px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #334155;
  }

  .section-head h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
</style>
